verbose_text: Premenstrual progesterone withdrawal increases levels of cyclo-oxygenase (COX) 2 enzyme in the endometrium, which stimulates the synthesis of endometrial prostaglandins (PGs), including prostaglandin E 2 (PGE 2) and F 2alpha (PGF 2alpha).
